* In-session command history.
* Persistent history across restart when appropriate.
* Up and Down traversal.
* History cursor behavior that preserves the current unfinished command.
* Deduplication of adjacent identical entries.
* Configurable or bounded history size.
* Reverse search when practical.
* Cursor movement and editing.
* Home, End, word movement, deletion, and escape behavior.
